Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:15.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在无法动弹 虽说这是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:20.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不言放弃 因为已经觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:25.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸中燃起激情 撰写着时代的印迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:30.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜艳的颜色 熊熊燃烧的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:35.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭 现在已经看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:40.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找寻 路标浮现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:43.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要有自己的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:47.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有自己崇高的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:53.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那剩下的里面 选出年轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信Z标记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:01:00.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起 跨越艰难的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:06.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干裂的嘴唇 若是被滋润了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:11.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越此刻 向着火热的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:16.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进也好 都是因为坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信Z标记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:23.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起 跨越艰难的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:48.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Oh 我禁不住相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:55.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定会和你再见面 从那天起就一直坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:00.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定能呼唤到你 如果你还有心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:10.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}无限的力量 将你唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:16.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}啊 在你受到伤害前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:22.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}尽量 找寻 请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:27.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}不要丢弃 正是因为在这痛苦的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:31.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}总有一天会看见蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:38.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定的 直到和你一起看的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵达香港的阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇见了为去宇宙而等待船次的米莱母子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 从史多利出发的巨型MS 精神力高达入侵香港
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪对那个敌人抱有厌恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被俘的米莱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤 回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你擅自行动 我就不给你恢复记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是精神力的机师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把她带回来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的备件已经全部装载完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下飞行平台的搬运了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗商会真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见卡缪和阿姆罗先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在有点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住 捷米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我搭乘奥特姆拉是你的主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但隼人一定也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没拿到去宇宙的机票吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感谢你们啊 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战局越恶化 去宇宙就越困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 天知道什么时候才能见到布莱德先生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想和丈夫见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能因此把孩子们也卷入战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再考虑一下吧 阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 滑翔机飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上奥特姆拉就要离开这里了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水用高扎古3台 出击完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样你就满意了吧 康奈尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你投入这么多人力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们在凤的身上投入了大量资金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让各位特务人员寻找迷路的孩子让我很过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们这里也没有多余的人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 对我们来说这也是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能利用凤的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而完好无损地得到奥特姆拉号的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用火烧香港了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于提坦斯来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在香港进行特殊任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定要展现一下实际成绩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果凤是已完成的强化人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她一定会与敌人接触的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨博士是有才能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人既不是军人也不是奥古的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让他们搭乘奥特姆拉啊 阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥特姆拉…阿姆罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哥哥的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再弄丢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到滑翔机了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是阿姆罗·雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隼人馆长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗先生 为什么不做声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么操纵高达MKII的就是这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗先生默不做声地出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟着去就更令人担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来制止阿姆罗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请你立即回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我感到不快的人就是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能送我去旧城区吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识那对恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对互相舔伤口的男女…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗·雷和住在东方珊瑚号上带着两个小孩的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有私人关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢滑翔机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在天上飞的都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫卡缪 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凤·村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤·村雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难读的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人替我这么取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温柔的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢自己的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写在你脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么办才好啊 布莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去宇宙比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我把要洗的衣服拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捷米的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错 捷米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到凤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的无线通信能和广播电台接通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把凤怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是掐住奥古脖子的好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始之后 她就会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不下车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不请我喝点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有一家店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实话实说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里我就会去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算刚才那些人在的地方也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤是阿姆罗的崇拜者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:08:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会嫉妒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 其实我在找一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个理解我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请奥古及其相关人员听好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是史多利号代理舰长 本·沃德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果诸位不在24小时之内把奥特姆拉号交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将开始对新香港进行无差别攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果诸位卑鄙地发动攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将无法保证人质的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质是白色基地曾经的舰长布莱德·诺亚的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莱·矢岛和她的两个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要对孩子动手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去联络奥特姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是奥古的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶MS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会再见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉本·沃德 我最讨厌这种做法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的话就参加作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们擅自决定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临阵脱逃会被枪毙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在调查敌情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和我们这边的工作没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你看见我把奥特姆拉的机师引导这里来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是机师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用奥特姆拉进行交涉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等于眼睁睁地将这架加路达级交给敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他们手上有人质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是3 4个人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电话打进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是贝尔托琪卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有常识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然使用电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗先生他跑到敌人的气垫船上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我怎么劝他 他都不听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗他一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 贝尔托琪卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你直接回储备基地 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么感情用事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要忘记奥古的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去你们那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动奥特姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管是多么重要的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但决不能让香港陷入火海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要牵连罗商会的储备基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们的负责人出来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓交换人质是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿姆罗·雷大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人质应该不会不够格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得那张面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也不想被人说成是挟制妇女儿童作人质的卑鄙小人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们母子带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗真的来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见他的声音了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香港市长打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是奥特姆拉号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是斯蒂芬妮·罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各MS进入随时迎击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以罗商会的名誉保证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥特姆拉会离开香港的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样香港就不会被卷入战争了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莱夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥特姆拉里也有优秀的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和曾经的英雄在一起 真是荣幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么宁可这样也要把奥特姆拉弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不懂政治
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作为军人 服从军令是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当今的政府正在破坏着地球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莱夫人快点到陆地上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香港市的提案是对我们的侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奥特姆拉就这样离开香港的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将杀死4名人质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先将杀死布莱德·诺亚的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为能以机师的身份战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会参加这次作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且村雨研究所里有我重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了取回那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让本·沃德这样的俗人阻碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡缪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射飞行平台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 你终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了一名人质是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗本来打算用自己交换米莱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对方没有放人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗先生太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻举妄动会危及人质生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史多利号可能已经布下了陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没想过还会有史多利之外的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莱和阿姆罗都是重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一切顺利就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 国际都市香港也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于想到一个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用MKII既拯救人质又能拯救香港的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要交出奥特姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在投降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就前功尽弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能使用武力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以奥特姆拉要假装投降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我不会批准你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯蒂芬妮小姐没有这种权力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的时候冷静地观察战局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种温柔是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和凤不同的女人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人感觉到坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会救出大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯蒂芬妮小姐 感谢你费心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说了实话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人馆长 请告诉我出击的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没进行过水中机动性的测试…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意水压啊 卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也在水中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真老实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不用死了 大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥特姆拉来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如斯蒂芬妮小姐所说 还有其他的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了治好头痛 我还不能离开康奈尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人馆长 会提供支援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 那架大飞机里的叔叔们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会救阿姆罗叔叔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人这家伙 你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就知道我方没有战意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海中潜伏着敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卡缪他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来确实是投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫史多利来进行回收作业
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萨维
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萨维
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决了一台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让人质逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿姆罗先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:18:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莱夫人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水中用的MS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萨维
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各MS 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥特姆拉 准备离水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 娜米卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然人质已经逃走了 那我们的作战就失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会心里觉得恶心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得把这家伙引出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次能轻松的时候 紧接着总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔托琪卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好…你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能着陆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像阿姆罗一样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他比我更有潜质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥你在驾驶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我哥哥也醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你出现之后 阿姆罗就忘记了奥古的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出这么危险的事情来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆罗不是这么脆弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔托琪卡 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 米莱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了阿姆罗和卡缪的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 你表现很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 阿姆罗大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 你才辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪和凤在被赐予的短短的时间之内
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能获得新的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香港的火海中 青春的青涩与懵懂消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:24:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人只看见了作为敌友而分离的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Zeta高达
